text:
There are certain points in one's life, some life turning decisions.One of it was me agreeing to go play water polo.Ye incident chipka hua hai dimag me, or rhe bhi kyu nhi, there i met You bhai<3. Us 1 hr me hi, we made small talks and i realised you already know everyone i know, in fact you even knew me!! :P. For me you were the first jisse ekdam se itne kam time me hi, itna strong connection bana. Gladly apne pe photo bhi hai tbki :P

In these 4 years, we‚Äôve shared almost all our lows and all our ‚Äòhighs‚Äô together. First year ki summers me D211 me gadda dal lia tha tune mere room me hi, din bhr bs binging on netflix and having snacks. Zsquare Mac lene gye the, rokde me payment kia :P, fir pizza hut pe party. Midsem and endsem ke time mere room pe bethke pdhna, sare last rush hour pe assignments likhna. Dange, tere or mere library me wo constant sessions, exam time night outs. Kitni numerous choti choti memories hai bro hmari. Random Lucknow trips, Chandu or tere sath rooftop pe meri pehli beer, Nh91 ka mera first hukka or fir supposedly meri chair ka hilna :P. Random bazooka and zsquare trips apni. That one day ramaiya pe cab leke aya tu, and tera wo ‚Äúwelcome to kanpur‚Äù sbse epic. Bhai its just tu sath hai na tab tak sb shi lgta, its like singh galat hone hi ni dega kuch, he‚Äôll handle everything somehow. <333. Remember ek din me aya tha tere room preshan, gusse me bhi kisi pe, and fir tune mujhe bitakhe samjhaya about the college life,life in general ,friends and the number of fingers we have on our hand. Will never forget that lesson. Cheers to all the innumerable parties,lectures, assignments, labs, fests, Music sessions and to the innumerable memories that we made along the wayü•Ç. 

You have always made me feel like home, in fact more than home, tune ek ‚Äúreal‚Äù brother ki kami puri kari hai meri life me. Mujhko jara si bhi preshani hoti thi ya dar lagta tha, ya anything, i always used to seek out for you first. Itne aasani se mujhe or meri life ki bt handle kse kr leta tha tu. You are the reason for most of the things or experiences that i‚Äôve managed to pull off in these 4 years, i just couldn‚Äôt have done all that by myself bro, tu sath rhta tha to ek confidence rhta tha. I've shared directly or indirectly my every ‚Äòfirst‚Äô experience of life with you. Bhut sare personal experiences as well as spiritual experiences.

Or han meri trip kharab nhi hui thi that day, and na kharab hone ka reason bhi tu hi hai, you said to me earlier ‚Äúapni trip ham khud drive krte hai‚Äù. I was so focused on this the whole time that i never went down. Infact the time when you, me and jayesh were in the Oat, wo moment mujhe lifetime yaad rhega, about the things we talked, and felt even without talking, about being there for each other no matter what. Baki we‚Äôll trip again sometime soon, some different place this time. You might not have an idea kitna impact hai tera meri life pe. We laughed together and cried together. We are spirit brothers and share a bond that's forever unbroken.

Baki bhai ye memoirs me nhi kr skta sab express, your‚Äôe too precious for that. I‚Äôve literally lost count teko kitni bar HC ya bhr Hospital leke aya hu. Abhi dur rhega to tbiyat ka khayal rkhna apna, tu kohinoor hai mera, bhut chamkna hai abhi life me aage. We‚Äôve shared a connection for a lifetime, abhi bhut punye or paap krne hai sath me ü•Ç. 

Perfect lines for this perfect brotherhood <3

text:
I remember we first met because of basketball, and also our roll nos were close so we were even in the same PE group bhai. Kafi entertaining rehta tha wo time because of you and your always ready witty puns and jokes. 

But things changed jab ham dono ne Summer camp join kia, I mean they really changed man!!.  For me personally it was one of the best time of my stay at IITK. Jannat tha bhai. And it was all because you were there, Bhut shi bonding kri hai bhai hmne us 1 mahine me. Subh uthate the ek dusre ko jse tese, Pura din pel ke basketball khelna subh or raat or bs bch me khana or wpis sona. In sab ke bch jo hamne bakchodiyan ki hai, will never forgot them. Sbse jyada tuning/sync court pe bhi tujhse bethti thi, cheers to both us rebounders. Bhut shi time tha yr wo, Truly it was more like a dream when I think of it now, and you have been a major part of it. Also yaad hoga Reading room me Ac ke chakkar me pde rhte the :P hall 2 ke. 

Apart from this apne paths kbhi na kbhi cross hote hi rhe kbhi arts ka course to kbhi kuch, and I‚Äôm so glad they did, infact last ke 1 months bhi hmko khelne ko mila, relive krne ko mila whi time phle wla, im so happy that happened. 

I can‚Äôt thank you enough for being a part of my life at IITK, I will always cherish the time I‚Äôve spent with you man! and I will always look forward to have more of it. You have such a warm and happy personality bro, also you‚Äôre an amazing artist . I cant afford to lose gems like you <3 . You‚Äôll do wonders in life, Stay in touch and Take care. 

PS ‚Äì Cheers to our 100 streak on snapchat <3 wpis ayega to fir bnaenge and  For every shot we missed  "Lakri ka board hota to jati !!!" :P
